{{Infobox bio | name = Fiorella Mattheis | image = Fiorella Matheis.jpeg | imagesize = 220px | birth_name = Fiorella Gelli Mattheis | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1988|02|10}} | birth_place = [[Petrópolis]], [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]], Brazil | residence = | nationality = | occupation = Actress, model | height = {{convert|1.75|m|ftin|abbr=on}} | spouse = [[Flávio Canto]] (2013–2014) }} '''Fiorella Gelli Mattheis''' (born February 10, 1988<ref name="thirteen" />) is a [[Brazil]]ian actress, model and television presenter.<ref name="thirteen">{{cite web|url=http://ego.globo.com/Gente/Noticias/0,,MUL1225945-9798,00-CONHECA+A+TRAJETORIA+E+SAIBA+COMO+E+A+ROTINA+E+A+INTIMIDADE+DE+FIORELLA+MAT.html|title=Conheça a trajetória e saiba como é a rotina e a intimidade de Fiorella Mattheis|accessdate=22 August 2015|date=19 July 2009|language=pt}}</ref>
== Biography == Fiorella was born in [[Petrópolis]], [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]]. She is of Italian and German ancestry, both her paternal and maternal family name are from Northern Italy.<ref name="one">{{cite web|url=http://diversao.terra.com.br/gente/noticias/0,,OI3571905-EI13467,00-Fiorella+Mattheis+nao+se+intimida+com+audiencia+de+Malhacao.html|title=Fiorella Mattheis não se intimida com audiência de 'Malhação'|accessdate=21 August 2015|date=27 May 2007|language=pt}}</ref><ref name="two">{{cite web|url=http://gshow.globo.com/programas/programa-do-jo/O-Programa/noticia/2014/11/fiorella-mattheis-revela-que-nao-queria-ser-modelo-odiava-tirar-fotos.html|accessdate=21 August 2015|date=22 November 2014|title=Fiorella Mattheis revela que não queria ser modelo: ‘Odiava tirar fotos’|language=pt}}</ref> She is the daughter of [[Andreas Mattheis]], a race car driver,<ref name="three">{{Cite web|url=http://ego.globo.com/Gente/Noticias/0,,MUL858364-9798,00-FIORELLA+MATTHEIS+FAZ+HOMENAGEM+AO+PAI.html|title=Fiorella Mattheis faz homenagem ao pai|date=11 November 2008|language=pt|accessdate=21 August 2015}}</ref> and Sandra Gelli Mattheis.<ref name="fourteen">{{Cite web|url=http://caras.uol.com.br/tv/fiorella-mattheis-posta-foto-com-mae-e-impressiona-por-semelhanca#.VdgGxbaj4pR|title=Fiorella Mattheis posta foto com a mãe e impressiona por semelhança|accessdate=22 August 2015|language=pt}}</ref> On July 20, 2013, she married [[Flávio Canto]];<ref name="four">{{cite web|url=http://ego.globo.com/famosos/noticia/2013/07/fiorella-mattheis-e-flavio-canto-se-casam-na-regiao-serrana-do-rio.html|accessdate=21 August 2015|date=20 July 2013|title=Fiorella Mattheis e Flávio Canto se casam na Região Serrana do Rio|language=pt}}</ref> they divorced in September 2014.<ref name="five">{{Cite web|url=http://entretenimento.r7.com/famosos-e-tv/saiba-o-que-pode-ter-motivado-a-separacao-de-fiorella-mattheis-e-flavio-canto-03092014|title=Saiba o que pode ter motivado a separação de Fiorella Mattheis e Flávio Canto|accessdate=20 August 2015|date=3 September 2014|language=pt}}</ref>
== Career ==
Mattheis began her modeling career at the age of fourteen, after being a finalist of a competition held by the agency [[Elite Model Management]]. Soon after she moved to [[São Paulo]], and it was from there that her career as a model took off. From fifteen to seventeen, she lived in Japan, Hong Kong and some European countries. Her acting career started when she played Vivian in [[Malhação]].<ref name="one" />
Mattheis does not consume [[alcoholic beverage]]s.<ref name="six" /> While she stopped eating red meat and chicken for ideological reasons two years ago, she otherwise avoids stringent dietary restrictions. Instead, she relies on an intense exercise regimen that she began as a teenager: "I run five to seven kilometers three to four times a week. Sometimes on the treadmill, sometimes outdoors." Mattheis has two [[personal trainer]]s.<ref name="twelve">{{cite web|url=http://diariogaucho.clicrbs.com.br/rs/entretenimento/noticia/2015/08/fiorella-mattheis-revela-como-mantem-a-forma-e-garante-odeio-ser-proibida-de-comer-4824120.html|title=Fiorella Mattheis revela como mantém a forma e garante: "Odeio ser proibida de comer"|accessdate=22 August 2015|date=13 August 2015|language=pt}}</ref> Mattheis attributes her successful career to achieving what could not be done with beauty alone through "hard work and dedication".<ref name="eighteen">{{Cite web|url=http://gshow.globo.com/programas/video-show/Por-tras-das-cameras/noticia/2015/03/fiorella-mattheis-revela-sonho-e-rejeita-rotulo-de-musa-so-beleza-nao-sustenta.html|title=Fiorella Mattheis revela sonho e rejeita rótulo de musa: 'Só beleza não sustenta'|accessdate=23 August 2015|date=16 March 2015|language=pt}}</ref>
In early June 2015, Mattheis was honored as the godmother of the [[non-governmental organization]] Ampara Animal in Rio de Janeiro for her activism in helping needy cats and dogs.<ref name="seventeen">{{Cite web|url=http://portaldodog.com.br/cachorros/celebridades/fiorella-mattheis-foi-eleita-madrinha-da-ong-ampara-animal-no-rio-de-janeiro/|title=Fiorella Mattheis foi eleita madrinha da ONG Ampara Animal no Rio de Janeiro|accessdate=23 August 2015|date=2 June 2015|language=pt}}</ref> Later that month, Mattheis had her hair treated by burning with a lit candle. This technique increases the strength and body with which hair grows, and should only be employed by qualified professionals.<ref name="sixteen">{{Cite web|url=http://ego.globo.com/beleza/noticia/2015/06/fiorella-mattheis-faz-velaterapia-nos-cabelos-e-brinca-aprontando.html|title=Fiorella Mattheis faz velaterapia nos cabelos e brinca: 'Aprontando'|accessdate=22 August 2015|date=12 June 2015|language=pt}}</ref> In July 2015, she posed in a bikini with fellow Vai Que Cola third season actress Samantha Schmutz.<ref name="fifteen">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ofuxico.com.br/noticias-sobre-famosos/fiorella-mattheis-e-samantha-schmutz-posam-de-biquini/2015/07/23-244230.html|title=Fiorella Mattheis e Samantha Schmutz posam de biquíni|accessdate=22 August 2015|date=23 July 2015|language=pt}}</ref>
In August 2015, Mattheis posed in an advertisement for the clothing brand PG with actor and designer Paulo Gustavo. Gustavo described Mattheis as "the most beautiful woman I've ever seen."<ref name="ten">{{cite web|url=http://epoca.globo.com/colunas-e-blogs/bruno-astuto/noticia/2015/08/paulo-gustavo-e-fiorella-mattheis-posam-para-marca-de-roupas-do-comediante.html|title=Paulo Gustavo e Fiorella Mattheis posam para marca de roupas do comediante|accessdate=21 August 2015|date=19 August 2015|language=pt}}</ref>
